tool_description: Returns the list of all optimal solutions ( QTM not HTM ) for a given pocket cube ( 2x2x2 ) position.
title: Pocket Cube Solver

api_list.name: getRandomSolution
api_list.description: Returns json data consisting of a random optimal solution of a given cube position.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://pocket-cube-solver1.p.rapidapi.com/{position}/random"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "pocket-cube-solver1.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
